{"title_page": "Patterson Johnson", "text_new": "{{short description|Bahamian triple jumper}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2020}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name        = Patterson Johnson\n| full_name   = \n| image       = \n| caption     = \n| nationality = Bahamian\n| sport       = Athletics\n| event       = Triple jump\n| club        = \n| collegeteam =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1964|8|26|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = \n| death_date  = \n| death_place = \n| height      =\n| weight      =\n}}\n\n'''Patterson Johnson''' (born 26 August 1964) is a Bahamian [[Sport of athletics|athlete]]. He competed in the [[Athletics at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's triple jump|men's triple jump]] at the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/jo/patterson-johnson-1.html |title=Patterson Johnson Olympic Results |accessdate=25 December 2017}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Johnson, Patterson}}\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Bahamian male triple jumpers]]\n[[Category:Olympic athletes of the Bahamas]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n{{Bahamas-athletics-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Bahamian triple jumper}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=December 2017}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name        = Patterson Johnson\n| full_name   = \n| image       = \n| caption     = \n| nationality = Bahamian\n| sport       = Athletics\n| event       = Triple jump\n| club        = \n| collegeteam =\n| birth_date  = {{birth date and age|1964|8|26|df=yes}}\n| birth_place = \n| death_date  = \n| death_place = \n| height      =\n| weight      =\n}}\n\n'''Patterson Johnson''' (born 26 August 1964) is a Bahamian [[Sport of athletics|athlete]]. He competed in the [[Athletics at the 1988 Summer Olympics \u2013 Men's triple jump|me